sourcesContent: import { html, ref, slotted } from "@microsoft/fast-element"; import { endSlotTemplate, startSlotTemplate } from "../patterns/start-end.js"; /** * The template for the {@link @microsoft/fast-foundation#(Anchor:class)} component. * @public */ export const anchorTemplate = (context, definition) => html ` ${startSlotTemplate(context, definition)} ${endSlotTemplate(context, definition)} `;
